This is a simple example of connecting to Gmail using the JavaMail Api

JavaMail api:  http://javamail.kenai.com/nonav/javadocs/index.html
               http://www.oracle.com/technetwork/java/faq-135477.html#gmail


This project is built using Gradle, and written in Groovy.

You will need to drop a config file at /tmp/emailtest.properties.  Look for the format in the exampleConfig directory.

There is a "Test" that demonstrates working the class.  You should be able to run it within eclipse or gradle.


http://bowerstudios.com/node/898

